lol_descInfo: Get information about the module "League of Legends".
lol_descElo: Get ranking information from a player. (?lol-elo SUMMONERNAME [SERVER=euw])
lol_descMatch: Get information about a current match. (?lol-match SUMMONERNAME [SERVER=euw])
lol_descVersion: Get the current version of the game.
lol_info: The module "League of Legends" adds additional commands for the same-named game.
